# Task 1
A simple command line application that consumes a Public API using a HTTP client library.

#Solution
My solution is a simple Slack Bot, That is conected to my team on slack called "Andela Api Test"

- Its Developed using the Slack Api 
- Its Invited to my #random channel
- Its Innitialised from my command line with the help of the "Slack bot Token" and the "Bot id"
- It performs a very simple task which is respond with "Come on maan,  do that Yourself!" whenever its referred and the start word is "do"

Otherwise it instructs you to send your command starting with the ketword "do"
